q1.index: How to earn crypto with the PTC ads?
q1.answer: Very easy, simply follow these steps:
q1.one: Go to the Earning tab and switch to the Paid ADS section. The paid ads available to you will be shown with the timers on them, click the one you want to visit.
q1.two: Wait for the website to load and the timer to start counting down. Please, consider checking the content of the service offered out while the timer is running.
q1.three: The window with the ad must be in focus for the length of the visit.
q1.four: After the timer counts down, complete the captcha to earn the reward.
q1.five: Once you have received your tokens, feel free to either close the ad and return to the hub or continue to browse the advertised site.

q2.index: Can I get paid for viewing ads with cryptocurrencies or just with the Freebitme tokens?
q2.answer: Freebitme tokens only, you can exchange Freebitme tokens any time to any cryptocurrency supported, here: exchange

q3.index: The website is blank when I clicked on an ad and the timer is not starting, what to do?
q3.answer: Wait for the website to load and for the timer to count down and collect your reward. Then report it to us by clicking the report button or by opening a ticket.

q4.index: Why does the ad timer countdown sometimes take longer than it says?
q4.answer: The ad timer won't not start until the ad page has fully loaded.

q5.index: How do I know I got credited for viewing an ad?
q5.answer: A green notification panel will appear at the right top corner of the page showing your reward in Freebitme for viewing this ad.

q6.index: Can I pay for ads with cryptocurrencies or just with the Freebitme tokens?
q6.answer: Freebitme tokens only, you can exchange Freebitme tokens any time to any cryptocurrency supported here:

q7.index: How do I advertise on the Paid ads section?
q7.answer: Very easy, simply follow these steps:
q7.one: Go to the Earning tab and switch to the Paid ADS section. Click on the Manage ads tab.Go to the Campaigns tab and click the New campaign button.
q7.two: Please, read carefully the instructions and guidelines on the right side of the page. Rule violations could result in your ad not approved and even your account being banned.
q7.three: Fill out the required information, including the name of your ad (only visible to you) ad URL, ad title, ad description...
q7.four: Click Create button - your ad campaign will be submitted for approval. Your ad campaign will be approved within 24 hours, usually much faster than that
q7.five: After your ad campaign has been approved, you can create new and manage old ads on the Adverts tab.
q7.six: Go to the Adverts tab, click New Advert, choose the campaign you want to advertise from the drop down menu (if you have more than one) and fill out the required info: the number of views you want to purchase, view duration, the time period your ad will be shown to a user: once a 24 hour, once 48 hrs or only once, choose geotargeting from the options listed and pick the features to make your ad stand out.
q7.seven: Click create and your ad is now live. You can pause/unpause it and view statistics of any of your ad on the Adverts page.

q8.index: How long does it take for my ad campaign to be approved?
q8.answer: Your ad should be approved or rejected within 24 hours, usually much faster.

q9.answer: You either violated the rules or didn't follow the guidelines. Please, make sure you read the rules on the ad campaign creation page carefully.

service2.title: Create a faucet
service2.subtitle: create a faucet using a faucet script other than Hostobit
service2.subtitle2:
Here you can create a faucet using any of the faucet scripts you like.
Follow these steps:
Fill in the faucet name, the faucet's URL and claim timer in seconds fields.
Select your faucet's currency, enter the claim reward (please, input the minimal available claim reward if your faucet supports multiple rewards or jackpots) and choose if you want your faucet to be listed on Freebitme or not
Click Create button and you will be given an API key which you can use to connect your faucet to Freebitme.
Now you can go back to the Site owner tab and top up/withdraw funds, check the stats, edit or archive your faucet.
Please, read carefully the instructions and guidelines on the right side of the page. Rule violations could result in your faucet refused service and/or removed from the faucet list.
service2.subtitle3:
No malicious websites.
No malware, viruses, spyware or ransomware.
No unsolicited or automated downloads.
No browser locking scripts or other attempts to hijack the browser.
Warning! We reserve the right to refuse service at our discretion. If we detect a malicious code or attempts to defraud the users, your account could be banned with any funds on it forfeit.

service3.title: Create another service
service3.subtitle: if you want to use our API (and your site is NOT a faucet) this option is for you
service3.subtitle2:
How does it work?
Here you can connect our API to a service/site of your choice.
A good example would be a cryptocurrency game, a banner network or any other site that pays micropayments in cryptocurrencies to multiple users.
To connect your site to our API and start using our hub as the payment gateway, follow these steps:
Fill in the site's name (only visible to you), the site's URL.
Click Create button and you will be given an API key which you can use to connect your site to Freebitme.
Now you can go back to the Site owner tab and top up/withdraw funds, check the stats, edit or archive your service/site.
Please, read carefully the instructions and guidelines on the right side of the page. Rule violations could result in your faucet refused service and/or removed from the faucet list.
